subject: Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Dog Sledding
lead_paragraph: Dallas Seavey was leading the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race, but Aliy Zirkle was close on his heels, leaving the village of Koyuk about 20 minutes later.
